  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"node__content\"> <section class=\"detail-page-head full-width-block\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-12\"> <small>Oaktree Capital- <span class=\"field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden\"><time class=\"datetime\" datetime=\"2024-08-23T15:47:00+00:00\" title=\"Friday, August 23, 2024 - 15:47\">Fri, 08/23/2024 - 15:47</time></span></small><h1><span class=\"field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden\">Navigating the Sea Change with Howard Marks at Oaktree Conference 2024</span></h1></div></div></div> </section> <section class=\"detail-page\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-8-lg\"><div class=\"feature-image-visability\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-banner field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default insurance-library-image\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\"><div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div><div class=\"field__item\"> <img alt=\"Featured\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid\" data-src=\"/sites/default/files/2024-08/OaktreeFeatured2.jpg\" height=\"381\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2024-08/OaktreeFeatured2.jpg\" width=\"908\"/></div></div> </article></div></div><div class=\"audio-player\"></div><div style=\"padding:56.25% 0 0 0;position:relative;\"></div><p>On April 10, <strong>Howard Marks</strong> opened Oaktree Conference 2024 in Los Angeles with a deep dive into his sea change thesis, exploring the broad implications for the investment world. You can now watch an excerpt of this talk. <br/> </p><div class=\"avalible-pods\"><div class=\"block block-block-content block-block-content9a03abe3-6e62-4857-9ccf-a8978d7294f7\" id=\"block-podcastisavailableon\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-link-with-image field--type-entity-reference-re